<title type="html"><![CDATA[4/24(Sat.)Teen's driving ban after boy's skull fractured in e-scooter crash/Do you expect this technology?(Host:Danny)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=493&amp;p=515#p515"><![CDATA[
4/24(Sat.)Teen's driving ban after boy's skull fractured in e-scooter crash/Do you expect this technology?(Host:Danny)<br /><br />Session 1:<br />Teen's driving ban after boy's skull fractured in e-scooter crash<br /><a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-leicestershire-56724347" class="postlink">https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-leicestershire-56724347</a><br /><br />Discussion<br />1. What do you think after reading the article?<br />2. Do you think Taiwan is suitable for opening up electric scooters?<br />3. Do you have any experience or stories about emerging vehicles? (e.g. Segway)<br /><br /><br />Session 2:<br />Monkey MindPong<br /><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rsCul1sp4hQ&amp;ab_channel=Neuralink" class="postlink">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rsCul1sp4hQ&amp;ab_channel=Neuralink</a><br /><br />Discussion<br />1. Do you expect this technology to become a product?<br />2. What product will it be?<br />3. What is the worst case scenario?<br /><br /><br />///////////////////////////////////////////////////////<br />Agenda<br />7:00 ~ 7:30 pm greetings &amp; free talk<br />7:30 ~ 8:15 pm guests introduced &amp; first session discussion<br />8:15 ~ 8:45 pm presentation, sharing the article &amp; other experiences<br />8:45 ~ 9:30 pm second session discussion<br /><br />Position: Dante coffee Shop (丹堤咖啡), MRT板南線 - 新埔站2號出口, next to 7-Seven,<br />板橋民生路二段237 號,<br />Time: PM 7:00-9:30,<br /><br />P.S.<br />1.因聚會地點是在咖啡店內，所以有低消80元喔！<br />2.參加三次後，只要繳交1000元 (學生:500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />3.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Wed Apr 21, 2021 2:46 am</p><hr />
